          "plain_text": "I’m feeling uncomfortably full after all the noodles last night so just opt for some coffee to start the morning. I come up to the sun room and bump into Lisa. We end up having an incredible conversation relating to mindfulness and basically all things concerning the human experience. She’s simultaneously assured of her knowledge while also being inquisitive for anything new.",
