          "plain_text": "Cuan comes walking in with his dog and sits down at the table with me. He’s the guy trying to build the water tank on his property. We get talking and go down the conversation of his work and life before moving here. He worked in IT and is now learning to code in his little hut. I’m also amused to find out that he spends quite a bit of time trying to hack into the local networks in the Transkei.",
